title: NASA, Gulf of Mexico BP Oil Platform Oil Spill Contours, World, April 2010
name: NASA, Gulf of Mexico BP Oil Platform Oil Spill Contours, World, April 2010
description: These contours were generated from the point shape file of the BP oil spill, which was created from NASA's satellite photo of the GOM area of 25th April, 2010. Look elsewhere on Finder! for the point shape file of the oil spill. Use key words: BP, Oilspill,  Maker! shows a combined map of the location of now sunk BP platform and the oil spill.
